{
  "id": "adv_main_01_07_06",
  "title": "星見編2章6話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4666666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ雌雄を決する時が\n来たみたいですわね、雫！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ the time has finally come\nto decide who will be the winner!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今日こそ決めますわよ\n私とあなた、どちらの方が…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s the day\nwe finally determine which of us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに詳しいのかを！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…knows more about idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "…………わかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.883333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "リアクション薄過ぎません！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with your dull reaction?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.883333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……なあ、二人は何してるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ what are you two up to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.99464858373006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さんお疲れさまです\n見ての通り……勝負？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hello‚ {user}-san.\nAs you can see… they’re competing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.49104309082031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "少し前に、{user}さんが\n言ってたお仕事ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the work you mentioned\nlast time‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.557709757486975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ネット放送局から持ち込まれた\nクイズ番組の企画です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thae quiz show which is\nfrom the internet broadcast station.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.72437642415365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、アイドルの知識を競うって、あれな\nさっそく、誰が出るか決めようとしてたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right‚ the one based on idol trivia.\nAre they already trying to decide who’ll participate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.55770975748699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。各事務所から代表一人って話だったので\n誰が出るべきかって相談してたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. The only one idol represents per company‚\nso we were discussing who should go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.59104309082032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私達は、その……雫ちゃんが詳しいし\nその方がいいんじゃって話してたんですけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-we think‚ well… Shizuku-chan knows a lot about idols‚\nso she’d probably be the best‚ but――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.52437642415365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとうるさいですわ、外野席！\nこれから神聖なる戦いが始まるというのにっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quiet down over there‚ you bystanders!\nOur holy battle is about to begin!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.05770975748699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふっ！ テレビ出演を果たすチャンス……\n絶対に勝ってみせますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoo whoo! There’s absolutely no way I’m missing out\non this opportunity to be on TV!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.09104309082029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな……自分の方が詳しいからって\nすずが雫に挑戦状叩きつけたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… so Suzu is challenging Shizuku\nbecause she thinks she’s more knowledgeable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.15770975748696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……逆ですわ。挑戦者は雫の方\n星見プロの初代アイドルクイズ王者は私ですもの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What… It’s the opposite! Shizuku is the challenger.\nI am a Hoshimi Productions’ first Idol Quiz Champion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.42437642415362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "その初代って、いつ、どうやって決めたの……\n私、初耳なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First? When and where did that take place?\nThis is the first I’m hearing of it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.85770975748696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "野暮なツッコミはノーサンキューですわ！\nMCのくせに気の効いたコメントもできませんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t appreciate your heckling!\nEspecially since you’re supposed to be the host.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.44504797740646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい……わかりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine‚ fine… Alright.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1783813107398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう、早く始めますわよ！\n我が心のアイドルデータベースの真髄、披露しますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ come on‚ let’s hurry up and start this!\nLet me show you the essence of my idol database in my heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.71171464407308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "えー、ポイント10対1により\n第一回星見プロアイドルクイズ王決定戦……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehem. Well then‚ with a score of 10-1‚\nthe winner of the First Hoshimi Productions’ Idol Quiz Championship is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1117146440731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "兵藤雫の勝利",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Shizuku Hyodo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6117146440731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 127.8117146440731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでですのおおぉぉぉ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaat?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8117146440731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……勝った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I did it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.62155580007897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "凄まじいまでの圧勝だったな……\n怜が問題読み上げる前に答えて全問正解って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was an overwhelming victory…\nShizuku was answering all the questions correctly before Rei even finished reading them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.62155580007908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんも最後に一問正解したけど\nあれ……答えるのにずいぶん時間かかってたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan got one question right‚\nbut… she took a long time to answer it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.55488913341236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それってつまり\n雫ちゃんがお情けで待ってくれてた……ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-doesn’t that mean\nShizuku-chan delayed answering the question… out of pity?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0875021032989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあなんであれ\nこれで雫ちゃんが出場ってことで、決まりだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ in any case‚\nwe can all agree that Shizuku-chan will be the contestant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3548891334124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。月ストが出演するチャンスを逃したのは\n正直、悔しいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agreed. Although it’s a shame Moon Tempest\nmissed out on the opportunity‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.0882224667457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_06-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "正々堂々勝負した結果だから……\n頑張って、雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "she won fair and square.\nGood luck on the quiz‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.64239482366912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
